# Accordion — Style Spec

## CSS Classes

| Class | Element | Notes |
|-------|---------|-------|
| `.acko-accordion` | Root wrapper | `flex column`, full width |
| `.acko-accordion-item` | Each item section | `border-bottom` separator, last-child none |
| `.acko-accordion-item-disabled` | Disabled item | Muted text, `cursor: not-allowed` |
| `.acko-accordion-trigger` | Trigger button | Full-width flex row, `--font-body-md-size`, weight 500 |
| `.acko-accordion-chevron` | Icon wrapper | Rotate 180deg when open |
| `.acko-accordion-chevron-open` | Open state | `transform: rotate(180deg)` |
| `.acko-accordion-content-wrapper` | Animated container | `overflow: hidden`, `max-height` transition |
| `.acko-accordion-content` | Inner content | `--font-body-sm-size`, `padding-bottom: --space-4` |

## Animation
- Content reveal: `max-height` transition, 200ms `--ease-out-quad`
- Chevron rotation: 200ms `--ease-out-quad`
- Trigger hover color: 150ms ease

## Token Usage
- Text: `--color-text-strong`, `--color-text-default`, `--color-text-muted`, `--color-text-disabled`
- Borders: `--color-border-subtle`
- Hover: `--color-primary`
- Spacing: `--space-4`
- Font: `--font-body-md-size` (trigger), `--font-body-sm-size` (content)
